{"tid":1706821,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"淨係識唱第一段Do You Hear the People Sing 既入黎","createTime":"2019-11-11T07:28:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T15:43:19.000Z","uid":41423,"like":68,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"3c4d3fa49949c8aef01346ed28a9ed49e782faf0","tid":1706821,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T07:28:12.000Z","msg":"Do you hear the people sing,<br />\nsinging a so of angry men<br />\nIt is the music of a people who will not be slaves again,<br />\nWhen the beating of your heart echoes the beating of the drums<br />\nThere is a life about to start when tomorrow comes.<br />\n<br />\n好多人都識唱呢一段<br />\n但更多人唔明隻歌既重點係之後既歌詞！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Will you join in our crusade<br />\nWho will be strong and stand with me?<br />\nBeyond the barricade is there a world you long to see</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Then join in the fight that will give you the right to be free</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDo you hear the people sing,<br />\nsinging a song of angry men<br />\nIt is the music of a people who will not be slaves again,<br />\nWhen the beating of your heart echoes the beating of the drums<br />\nThere is a life about to start when tomorrow comes.<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Will you give all you can give so that the banner may advance?<br />\nSome will fall and some will live,<br />\nWill you stand up and take the chance?<br />\nThe blood of the Martys will water the meadows of France!</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nDo you hear the people sing,<br />\nsinging a song of angry men<br />\nIt is the music of a people who will not be slaves again,<br />\nWhen the beating of your heart echoes the beating of the drums<br />\nThere is a life about to start when tomorrow comes.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">和理非都要有行動升級意識，唔係口講唔割但就做free rider! 享受成果！真香港人唔能夠只等勇武付出汗血前途，唔能夠只等外國介入，而係要每人做多一步，對抗不公不義!</span>"},{"pid":"d711d334aa7ee735406d39edb01243168e9e7c98","tid":1706821,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T07:30:29.000Z","msg":"1/1000"},{"pid":"012ad7af4eb4f92451ed6fa7a360d73bb10cc6c6","tid":1706821,"uid":321977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T07:31:11.000Z","msg":"「突發」新神獸出現，神鳥鳳凰<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1706526\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1706526</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4f4d72128b00ca80fced1bc7f3c0f819e3eb0aa3","tid":1706821,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T07:42:07.000Z","msg":"2/1000"},{"pid":"44219447a55840a849e912ee9c0ba2eeb864a3d1","tid":1706821,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T07:50:11.000Z","msg":"3/1000"},{"pid":"0127512775957d8bad4dbc31befe4c7a12903c1c","tid":1706821,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:00:22.000Z","msg":"4/1000"},{"pid":"79b215ef1b65c4fa50a8ac8a590ebb8937410d26","tid":1706821,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:25:33.000Z","msg":"5/1000"},{"pid":"23298399e1245ad62881270e33363b83c5809faf","tid":1706821,"uid":202876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:32:17.000Z","msg":"we will live again in freedom in the garden of the lord<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"856a557e36bcd5bab92d4c279b726aaf5639c5d6","tid":1706821,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T11:56:34.000Z","msg":"6/1000"},{"pid":"225ca9b219f9d6bcc3b50dcfc5fa2ed38c507fee","tid":1706821,"uid":188006,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:00:44.000Z","msg":"紅字個段先係精髓<br />\n又容易洗腦<br />\n日日哼緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f96edde70268af10a57e7ecb0cf6a0f10e582f0","tid":1706